org.pepstock.charba.client.labels

Class LabelsOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.NativeObjectContainer
      • org.pepstock.charba.client.plugins.AbstractPluginOptions
        • org.pepstock.charba.client.plugins.AbstractPluginCachedOptions
          • org.pepstock.charba.client.labels.LabelsOptions

  • public final class LabelsOptions
extends AbstractPluginCachedOptions
    This is the object to map the LabelsPlugin.ID plugin options, both at chart and global level.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
